{"chapter_number":87,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":8,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"الأعلى","name_complex":"Al-'A`lá","name_simple":"Al-A'la","verses_count":19,"pages":[591,592],"meaning":{"text":"The Most High","en":"The Most High","id":"Yang Paling Tinggi"},"verses":[[[1,5949,"87:1","سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى",["Glorify the name of your Lord, the Most High,","Sucikanlah nama Tuhanmu Yang Mahatinggi,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[2,5950,"87:2","الَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ",["Who creates, then makes complete,","Yang menciptakan, lalu menyempurnakan (ciptaan-Nya)."],591,30,60,237,null,null],[3,5951,"87:3","وَالَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ",["And Who makes (things) according to a measure, then guides (them to their goal),","Yang menentukan kadar (masing-masing) dan memberi petunjuk,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[4,5952,"87:4","وَالَّذِي أَخْرَجَ الْمَرْعَىٰ",["And Who brings forth herbage,","dan Yang menumbuhkan rerumputan,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[5,5953,"87:5","فَجَعَلَهُ غُثَاءً أَحْوَىٰ",["Then makes it dried up, dust-colored.","lalu dijadikan-Nya (rumput-rumput) itu kering kehitam-hitaman."],591,30,60,237,null,null],[6,5954,"87:6","سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلَا تَنسَىٰ",["We will make you recite so you shall not forget,","Kami akan membacakan (Al-Qur'an) kepadamu (Muhammad) sehingga engkau tidak akan lupa,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[7,5955,"87:7","إِلَّا مَا شَاءَ اللَّهُ ۚ إِنَّهُ يَعْلَمُ الْجَهْرَ وَمَا يَخْفَىٰ",["Except what Allah pleases, surely He knows the manifest, and what is hidden.","kecuali jika Allah menghendaki. Sungguh, Dia mengetahui yang terang dan yang tersembunyi."],591,30,60,237,null,null],[8,5956,"87:8","وَنُيَسِّرُكَ لِلْيُسْرَىٰ",["And We will make your way smooth to a state of ease.","Dan Kami akan memudahkan bagimu ke jalan kemudahan (mencapai kebahagiaan dunia dan akhirat),"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[9,5957,"87:9","فَذَكِّرْ إِن نَّفَعَتِ الذِّكْرَىٰ",["Therefore do remind, surely reminding does profit.","oleh sebab itu berikanlah peringatan, karena peringatan itu bermanfaat,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[10,5958,"87:10","سَيَذَّكَّرُ مَن يَخْشَىٰ",["He who fears will mind,","orang yang takut (kepada Allah) akan mendapat pelajaran,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[11,5959,"87:11","وَيَتَجَنَّبُهَا الْأَشْقَى",["And the most unfortunate one will avoid it,","dan orang-orang yang celaka (kafir) akan menjauhinya,"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[12,5960,"87:12","الَّذِي يَصْلَى النَّارَ الْكُبْرَىٰ",["Who shall enter the great fire;","(yaitu) orang yang akan memasuki api yang besar (neraka),"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[13,5961,"87:13","ثُمَّ لَا يَمُوتُ فِيهَا وَلَا يَحْيَىٰ",["Then therein he shall neither live nor die.","selanjutnya dia di sana tidak mati dan tidak (pula) hidup."],591,30,60,237,null,null],[14,5962,"87:14","قَدْ أَفْلَحَ مَن تَزَكَّىٰ",["He indeed shall be successful who purifies himself,","Sungguh beruntung orang yang menyucikan diri (dengan beriman),"],591,30,60,237,null,null],[15,5963,"87:15","وَذَكَرَ اسْمَ رَبِّهِ فَصَلَّىٰ",["And magnifies the name of his Lord and prays.","dan mengingat nama Tuhannya, lalu dia shalat."],591,30,60,237,null,null],[16,5964,"87:16","بَلْ تُؤْثِرُونَ الْحَيَاةَ الدُّنْيَا",["Nay! you prefer the life of this world,","Sedangkan kamu (orang-orang kafir) memilih kehidupan dunia,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[17,5965,"87:17","وَالْآخِرَةُ خَيْرٌ وَأَبْقَىٰ",["While the hereafter is better and more lasting.","padahal kehidupan akhirat itu lebih baik dan lebih kekal."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[18,5966,"87:18","إِنَّ هَٰذَا لَفِي الصُّحُفِ الْأُولَىٰ",["Most surely this is in the earlier scriptures,","Sesungguhnya ini terdapat dalam kitab-kitab yang dahulu,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[19,5967,"87:19","صُحُفِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ وَمُوسَىٰ",["The scriptures of Ibrahim and Musa.","(yaitu) kitab-kitab Ibrahim dan Musa."],592,30,60,237,null,null]],[[[1,10,591,"&#xfb9f;","word","سَبِّحِ",["Glorify",""]],[2,10,591,"&#xfba0;","word","اسْمَ",["(the) name",""]],[3,10,591,"&#xf